      "text": "# Backtest trend following model\r\n\r\n- 1. tests image\r\n---\r\n\r\n- 2. tests image 2\r\n---\r\n\r\n- 3. tests sentence 3\r\n---\r\n\r\n- 4. Test anything\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n$$\\zeta(x) = \\frac{1}{a} \\sum^{N}_{k=0}{x^k}$$\r\n\r\n\r\n![Image](image.svg)\r\n\r\n\r\nCool here we can write different content !\r\n\r\n# I've another great idea to share !\r\n\r\n  - Meta strategy — HeritageReverseStrategy 15min, CUSUM 0.05 targets\r\n  - Two alpha nodes (Long + Short), equal weights 1.0\r\n  - RandomForest 500 estimators, ECDF transform, weekly walk-forward retrain\r\n  - Entry threshold 0.8, cancel 0.5, leverage-based sizing\r\n  - Backtest period matches model evaluation window (2025-01-01 to 2025-06-01)\r\n  - Universe — BTCUSDT + ETHUSDT (Binance UM)\r\n  - nemesis"
